cast.overview: Elastigirl springs into action to save the day, while Mr. Incredible faces his greatest challenge yet – taking care of the problems of his three children.
cast.title: Incredibles 2

cast.original_title: Tinker Bell and the Pirate Fairy
cast.overview: Zarina, a smart and ambitious dust-keeper fairy who’s captivated by Blue Pixie Dust and its endless possibilities, flees Pixie Hollow and joins forces with the scheming pirates of Skull Rock, who make her captain of their ship. Tinker Bell and her friends must embark on an epic adventure to find Zarina, and together they go sword-to-sword with the band of pirates led by a cabin boy named James, who’ll soon be known as Captain Hook himself.
cast.title: Tinker Bell and the Pirate Fairy

cast.original_title: The Witcher: Nightmare of the Wolf
cast.overview: Escaping from poverty to become a witcher, Vesemir slays monsters for coin and glory, but when a new menace rises, he must face the demons of his past.
cast.title: The Witcher: Nightmare of the Wolf

details.biography:
A.J. LoCascio (born July 11, 1987) is an American actor and director. He is known for his roles as Prince Lotor in Voltron: Legendary Defender and Marty McFly in Back to the Future: The Game.

Source: Wikipedia contributors. (2025, March 29). A.J. LoCascio. Wikipedia.
